    </articleReference>
    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Ultrasound and Laser as Stand-Alone Therapies for Myofascial Trigger Points: A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study.]]></Value>
    </articleTitle>
